			<h3>03 - Basic Attack</h3>
			<p>explanation</p>
			$$ BasicAttack=\left( \sum_{} AttackModifier \right)\left(3+0.03\times BasePower\right)$$
			<hr>
			<h3>04 - Bonus Attack</h3>
			$$ BonusAttack=BasicAttack\times \left(\frac{BonusPower}{100+BasePower} \right) $$
			<p>explanation</p>
			<hr>
			<h3>Total Attack</h3>
			<p>explanation</p>
			$$ TotalAttack=BasicAttack+BonusAttack $$
			<hr>
			<h3>05 - Base Endurance</h3>
			<p>explanation</p>
