			<h3>07 - Basic Defense </h3>
			<p>explanation</p>
			$$ BasicDefense=\left( \sum_{} DefenseModifier \right)\left(0.5+0.01\times BaseEndurance\right) $$
			<hr>
			<h3>08 - Bonus Defenser</h3>
			<p>explanation</p>
			$$ BonusDefense=BasicDefense\times \left(\frac{BonuEndurance}{100+BaseEndurance} \right) $$
			<hr>
			<h3>Total Defense</h3>
			<p>explanation</p>
			$$ TotalDefense=BasicDefense+BonusDefense $$
